title: The Best of the Worst of Teddy Butch
description: A friend of mine gave me a copy of this cd. I'm not real sure about the source, but this shit spread like wildfire once people started hearing this cd in my car. I haven't been able to find out who made it exactly, so if anyone has more information, make sure to comment. All i have to go by is the title that was creatively lightscribed on the cd.
